query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(DISTINCT id_paciente) as total_pacientes,
  COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN id_paciente LIKE 'MIG-%' THEN id_paciente END) as migrados,
  COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN id_paciente LIKE '2025-%' OR id_paciente LIKE '2026-%' THEN id_paciente END) as sistema_atual
FROM pacientes;
